videos.description: Jordan Bohannon misses on purpose to remain tied with Chris Street for the most consecutive free throws made in Iowa history at 34. Street never had a chance to extend his streak, dying in a car accident in 1993.
videos.headline: Bohannon honors Street's Iowa record by missing free throw
